generated_query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM cards WHERE "setCode" = 'CSP' AND "convertedManaCost" > 5 AND power IS NULL;

SELECT AVG(M.home_team_goal) as average_home_goals
FROM Match M
JOIN Country C ON M.country_id = C.id
WHERE C.name = 'Poland' AND M.season = '2010/2011'

SELECT zip_code.city, COUNT(member.member_id) as member_count 
FROM member 
JOIN zip_code ON member.zip = zip_code.zip_code 
GROUP BY zip_code.city 
ORDER BY member_count DESC 
LIMIT 1;

SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT a.molecule_id) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT molecule_id) FROM molecule WHERE label = '+')) AS hydrogen_percentage
FROM atom a
JOIN molecule m ON a.molecule_id = m.molecule_id
WHERE a.element = 'h' AND m.label = '+';
